line_2: Seven, slur a Six; Eleven: A Nick.

line_1: The Woman finds it all a Trick,
line_2: That He could swoon, when She was sick;

line_1: Some men employ their health, an ugly trick,
line_2: In making known how oft they have been sick,

line_1: "Then copies spread, there lies the trick,
line_2: "For all who read will soon grow sick,

line_1: Let Them with BROWNE contrive, no vulgar trick,
line_2: To cure the dead, and make the living sick;

line_1: If they were not his own by finessing and trick;
line_2: Tho' secure of our hearts, yet confoundedly sick,
